item.description:
The first step in creating a new Canvas course that you want to connect to a Codio course, is connecting the Canvas course to the Codio Organization.
Install Codio By default, Codio is not an installed app on Canvas. You will need to install the app. Once you install it, you will be prompted to enter the &lsquo;Consumer Key&rsquo; and &lsquo;Secret Key&rsquo;
Tip Canvas&rsquo;s &ldquo;Add App&rdquo; is requesting Codio&rsquo;s &ldquo;Organization&rdquo; information.
